      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "\nHow is this space different than other spaces within gaming or speedrunning scenes? Could you tell us a little bit about the ways speedrunning scenes have been or continue to be exclusionary?"
